”) if you are a resident of Utah, acting in an individual or household context (and
not
in a commercial or employment context) your rights with respect to your personal data are described below. “
Personal Data
” refers that is linked or reasonably linkable to an identifiable individual, and does not include de-identified data and publicly available data.
